 from rei tsl cl nec co jp rei hamakawa subject xavier av extension to interviews article i d tsl one nine nine three apr two seven zero four three one one two two five zero five two organization c c systems research labs nec corporation kawasaki japan lines five eight nntp posting host hyperion tsl cl nec co jp dear folks it s a pleasure to be able to announce the release of a new freeware program xavier an audio and video extension to interviews xavier extension av class for interviews is a c class library that adds multimedia capability to interviews it allows composite multimedia objects to be built from media objects specifically it adds audio and video objects to the classes available in interviews three zero one three one and it does so without changing the source code for the original classes though several configuration files for interviews need to be changed via a patch file currently the xavier audio classes are only supported on sun workstations with an audio interface such as the sparcstation two xavier has been tested in the following environments sun machine sparcserver four seven zero sparcstation ipc os sun os four one one or later c sun c ver two one nec ews machine ews four eight zero zero two one zero two three zero os ews ux v rel four zero wsos four one release five one release five two c c release three one it can be obtained via anonymous ftp from interviews stanford edu in pub contrib xavier large demo tar and xavier tar we are preparing a mailing list for information regarding xavier if you are interested please contact xavier tsl cl nec co jp i will add your e mail address to our list reference o rei hamakawa hizekazu sakagami jun rekimoto audio and video extension to graphical interface toolkits the third international workshop on network and operating system support for digital audio and video san diego one nine nine two rei hamakawa e mail rei tsl cl nec co jp o o c c systems research laboratories o nec corporation o one one miyazaki fo